Rajasthan Travel Point is one of the leading car rental company and car hire service provider not only in Jaipur but in many states of Rajasthan.
We provide you all types of transportation services like buses, Tempo, Traveler for any yatra, tour or any special occasion. We also work with event companies and currently we have tie up with many event companies as their logistics manager.
